\section{Summary of Previous Presentation}

Mr.~Yu Hong presented the Testing Techniques, which is structured by three parts, Test Planning, Test Implementation and Test Results. Mr ~Yu Hong presented the big picture of the test planning in terms of Gantt Chart. And actually it is divided by two components, Implementation and Unit Testing and Integration and System Testing. They will carry out from Mid-break first week till week 12 and week 9 till week 12 respectively. He also demonstrated there are two phases in terms of Test Implementation, Informal Testing and Formal Testing. The former one consists of Hardware Testing in terms of robot prototype and robot functioning and Software Testing in terms of tests when coding while the latter one is made up of waterfall model and junit testing. The client was overall happy with the presentation.


